Abjuration
Level: Druid 6, Ranger 4
Components: V,S
Range: Personal
Target: You
Duration: 24 hours

This spell draws upon the natural reflexes of hunters and prey, giving you the ability to react to danger as more primitive beings might. You gain a +5 bonus on Reflex saves.

<i>A shower of sparks flies off your shoulders, cascading to the ground and clinging to your arms and legs.</i>